Completely agree with everything you said... i finished this game on medium difficulty in about 5 or 6 hours. I guess when you're used to playing games like FO3, and Just Cause, Mass Effect, Dragons Age, etc, etc, games like this just seem like a waste of time. They could have made it so much better... Oh, well, definitely not going to bother buying this one.

