@lukegoodman2001

Perhaps your computer can't handle the game? It was fine for me, stayed at a steady 30FPS for most of the gameplay... dropped down a little here and there. As for the cannon part, i posted above that you will have to start from a previous save file(not the same one), it's a bug that should fix itself... hopefully. You must take the power cell out of the furthest cannon... if you can't remove it, then the bug is still there and you will have to go back to a different save and play through again.

@smekjens

Can't help you, both my mouse and controller worked fine throughout the game... have you tried googling it?

@coolguy LTwin

start->run-> type in "regedit" hit "OK"

once in the registry look for "lucasarts" or "unleashed" in the registry and delete every and any entry you find. that MAY allow you to reinstall the game...
